external_knowledge:
- "digital garden" refers to the collection of games and their associated reviews and suggestions;
- "landscape" includes the number of reviews, suggestions, and the status of the reviews (approved or rejected);
- "names of the games" refers to the `game_title` column;
- "average ratings" refers to the average `rating` given by users, with a default of 0 if no ratings are available.

- A 'rating' of 4 or higher indicates a positive review;
- An 'approved' review status means the review has been reviewed and accepted by the moderators;
- An 'implemented' suggestion status means the user's suggestion has been acted upon and integrated into the game or platform.

- "shining stars" refers to the top-rated reviews;
- "wise souls" refers to the users who wrote the reviews;
- "suggestions" refer to the feedback or recommendations given to the reviews.

- 'average_rating' is the mean of all ratings given by users for a game;
- 'total_reviews' is the total number of reviews posted for a game;
- 'total_suggestions' is the total number of user suggestions provided for a game;
- 'game_title' is the title of the game.

- 'Risen above the waves' refers to games that have more than two approved reviews;
- 'Average rating that sparkles' refers to the average rating of the game;
- 'Glowing, approved reviews' refers to reviews with a status of 'approved'.

- 'stands out as the shining star' refers to the game with the highest average rating;
- 'user suggestions' are indicated by the `user_suggestion` column being 1;
- 'reviews approved' are indicated by the `review_status` column being 'approved'.

- 'Top-rated' refers to the highest-rated reviews within each game;
- 'Approved' refers to reviews that have been approved by the platform;
- 'Implemented suggestions' are user suggestions that have been acted upon and marked as implemented;
- 'More than one review' means the game has received at least two reviews.

- "blossoms" refers to reviews;
- "seeds of user suggestions" refers to reviews where the user has provided a suggestion (user_suggestion = 1);
- "garden of gaming" refers to the collection of games.

- 'player' is one of the roles a user can have in the system;
- 'suggestion' means the user has provided additional feedback or recommendations in the review;
- 'past five years' is determined by the current year minus 5.

sql:
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT game_id) AS game_count
FROM reviews
WHERE year = 2023 AND review_status != 'rejected';

